Anneke Wills https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anneke_Wills 0 Anneke Wills (born Anna Katarina Willys, 20 October 1941) is an English actress, best known for her role as the Doctor Who companion Polly in the long-running BBC science fiction television series Doctor Who.
